# Parizh, Kiginsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Parizh () is a rural locality (a village) in Nizhnekiginsky Selsoviet, Kiginsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 25 as of 2010.
Geography
Parizh is located  north of Verkhniye Kigi (the district's administrative centre) by road. Nizhniye Kigi is the nearest rural locality.
